column5: Its that time of year again to begin thinking of baseball! So, once again this year I am running a Yahoo pool. You will need a yahoo account to get in to it. It is free as always, with bragging rights on the line!!  Here is the info to log in.  http://baseball.fantasysports.yahoo.com/b2  League ID#: 125017 Password: lacrosse  Good luck!!!  Denis
